# Gerenciamento do Jogo
# Para todos os endpoints informar: /game/{room code}/{gamer id}

### Pega os dados do jogador.
GET http://localhost:8888/game/3195DB/3
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{auth}}

### Permite o início do jogo
GET http://localhost:8888/game/3195DB/3/allow
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{auth}}

### Avança a fase
POST http://localhost:8888/game/3195DB/3
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{auth}}
